profile:
OGC - Ottawa General Contractors are leaders as Ottawa's design and build renovation experts. Specializing in home renovations, new and custom home construction as well as home design. With our project management and coordination, we're able to efficiently juggle more jobs, large and small, without dropping the ball. 

Ottawa General Contractors are an accredited business with the Ottawa BBB and our CEO, Moe Abbas is a former member of the board of directors for the Better Business Bureau (BBB).. Our skills and expert service has allowed us to expand to other cities in Canada including Vancouver and Calgary in less than 8 years making us one of the fastest growing construction companies. 

We offer warranty following the Tarion warranty guidelines for all our renovations and construction projects. We also have a design center and in house designers available to help you design and build your home. With over 50 years of experience, our team has the knowledge, the tools, the skill-set and the resources to give you the best value for your dollar at unbeatable service. 

We at Ottawa General Contractors understand that you are looking for value with your renovation services. Trust our team to do it right the first time! Call us directly at (613) 225-9991!

Visit our website for all our credentials and more information.

profile:
Renovation and Disaster Recovery Services

Ever since its beginning, Renovco promptly became the leader in renovation and restoration services in the greater Montreal area. We’re proud to also be servicing the Ottawa/Gatineau and surrounding areas.

The full spectrum approach adopted by Renovco’s Management, from being general contractors to restoration experts to a fully equipped design center has earned Renovco the spot lead in the construction field.

It has received several remarkable recognitions from reputable institutions such as Canadian Business Magazine: PROFIT500: Fastest Growing Companies in Canada as well as Consumer Choice Award for the past 4 consecutive years. Nonetheless, it has also obtained accreditation from different Professional establishments such as the IICRC (Clean Trust Certified) and the OCCQ (Quebec’s BBB: A1 Rating).

Today, Renovco offers a wide range of services covering residential, commercial and industrial sectors.

Its field of expertise includes all types of renovation and design service, general contracting, mold remediation, post-disaster restoration and clean up content handling, and warehousing.

Renovco holds quality and customer convenience at heart. Along with its wide experience, Renovco brings in its human touch by providing personalized attention to every project; preserving the integrity and the soul of every house and building.

Renovco owes its success to the competency and skill of its professional teams and the trust of customers.

Our teams of experts are always ready to serve you, whether you would like to design your dream kitchen, remodel a bathroom, finish the basement, create a new home extension, renovate your office or get your home restored after a flood or fire, you can count on Renovco!

Renovco has a smartly identifiable Unique Concept. From emergency work reconstruction, content handling, and cleaning, warehousing, mold remediation, Ozone treatment, and Fire-åline system to a distribution channel and one-stop-shop for design services. This clever solution is translating to become, not only an exclusive competency that Renovco enjoys but also a profound peace-of-mind feature that clients treasure.
